      "type": "table_cell",
      "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": [139], "bgColor": null, "verticalAlign": null},
      "content": "**场景四：非阶梯退-可免费取消**\n\n退款规则为非阶梯退，当前仍在免费取消时间窗口内"
    },
    {
      "type": "table_cell",
